Vibrant paisley motifs entwine on a rich silk tie hand-printed in the Lake Como region of Italy using 15 separate silk-screens. Founded in northern Italy in 1910, Ermenegildo Zegna began as a woolen mill, which soon became known for producing beautiful, high-quality textiles—identified then and now by a signature red seal. The company’s expertise in quality materials persists to this day and can be found in every product they make.
  • 3 1/2" width; 59" length.
  • 100% silk.
  • Dry clean.
  • By Ermenegildo Zegna; made in Italy.
  • Men's Furnishings.

desc:

  • Dry clean.
  • By Etro; made in Italy.

name: Ralph Lauren Purple Label Solid Knit Silk Tie
desc:
Handcrafted in Italy, this impeccable tie features the ultra-luxurious texture of knit silk.
  • Handmade in Italy exclusively for Purple Label.
  • Jersey-knit and purple silk taping at the collar area for a smooth drape.
  • Unlined.
  • 2½" wide. 100% silk. Dry clean. Made in Italy.

name: Polo Ralph Lauren Striped Silk Repp Tie
desc:
Crafted from the finest silk repp, this Italian-made tie features a classic striped pattern.
  • Handmade with a fully fitted interlining to ensure a beautiful drape and a smooth, even knot.
  • Tip is lined with pure silk twill, which is a hallmark of superior necktie construction.
  • 3½" wide. 100% silk. Dry clean. Made in Italy.

name: Polo Ralph Lauren Solid Knit Silk Tie
desc:
The distinctive texture of pure knit silk lends a sophisticated touch to our classic tie.
  • Silk grosgrain taping at the collar ensures a smooth drape.

  • 100% silk. Dry clean. Imported.

name: Polo Ralph Lauren Paisley Wool Challis Tie
desc:
This Italian-made tie is crafted from soft wool challis and features a vintage-inspired paisley pattern.

  • Tip is lined with pure silk twill, which is a hallmark of superior necktie construction.

name: Marwood Striped Wool and Cotton-Blend Tie
desc:
Marwood 's wool and cotton-blend tie is the ideal companion to simple suiting in the cooler months. With an emphasis on traditional British craftsmanship, the expertly hand finished design is complete with the brand's signature diamond-pattern lining. We like that the diagonal stripes bring contemporary appeal to boardroom attire. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Black and light-grey striped wool and cotton-blend tie
  • 60% wool, 40% cotton
  • Dry clean
  • Made in England

name: Penrose Embroidered Woven-Silk Tie
desc:
Penrose 's exquisite ties are crafted on a jacquard loom by silk weavers and finished in England by artisanal craftsmen, making them an ideal gift for dapper gentlemen. This purple embroidered style is the perfect choice for introducing a dose of luxurious colour into your tailored looks. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Purple and black embroidered silk tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in England

name: Charvet Patterned Silk Bow Tie
desc:
Dapper gents have long relied on Parisian brand Charvet 's luxurious ties for formal wear. This navy bow tie is woven from pure silk with tiny, colourful polka dots embroidered across. Slip yours on with a white shirt and dark suit for instant panache.
  • Navy silk bow tie
  • Green, light-blue and pink polka dots, pre-tie style, adjustable neck strap
  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in France

name: Lanvin New Alber Silk-Satin Bow Tie
desc:

  • Pastel blue silk-satin bow tie
  • Pre-tied style, adjustable neck strap, hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in France

name: Drake's Silk-Grenadine Tie
desc:
Grenadine silk ties are an essential element for any well-dressed gent's repertoire, as the textured fabric can be worn for both smart and informal occasions. This navy version from British brand Drake's is a case in point. Balance the dark, solid colour with a striped shirt to give an elegant contrast. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Dark navy silk-grenadine tie
  • Fully lined
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in London

name: Charvet Houndstooth Silk and Wool-Blend Tie
desc:
Stand out in Charvet 's handsome navy and grey tie. Handcrafted in France, it's intricately woven in a houndstooth pattern and works best with dark suiting. Try it with a navy blazer for your next meeting. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .

name: Alexander McQueen Skull Silk-Jacquard Bow Tie
desc:
If you're looking for a way to add rebel flair to sleek formalwear, Alexander McQueen 's skull-jacquard bow tie is the answer. Crafted in Italy from pure silk, it won't fail to elevate your tailoring. Complete a debonair outfit with silver cufflinks and polished Oxford shoes.Shown here with a Charvet shirt .

  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

desc:
Patterned with signature skulls, Alexander McQueen 's neat bow tie will inject sleek formal attire with rakish flair. This navy piece is made in Italy from pure silk and has an adjustable strap for ease and comfort. Team it with a razor-sharp tuxedo at your next party.

name: Turnbull & Asser Ribbed Silk Tie
desc:
Each Turnbull & Asser silk tie is individually handmade in London, England to ensure high quality and an impeccable finish. Its ribbed appearance will add subtle flair to your most formal looks. Shown here with a Charvet shirt . The slimmer width of this tie is exclusively for MR PORTER.

name: Brooks Brothers Cotton-Piqué Bow Tie
desc:
A bow tie is the apex of elegance, and as cotton-piqué has been the fabric of choice for white tie events since the 1930s, you can rest assured this hand-tied Brooks Brothers piece won't let you down. Match the fabric to your waistcoat and shirt for a faultless formal look.

  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% cotton
  • Dry clean
  • Made in the USA

name: Charvet Knitted Silk Tie
desc:
Heritage Parisian company Charvet is globally renowned for its high quality materials and expert construction, aptly demonstrated by this impeccable knitted silk tie. This piece is flawlessly constructed in Italy in a slim profile that works best with streamlined silhouettes. Gift it to the gentleman who appreciates luxurious details with panache. Shown here with a Charvet shirt .
  • Yellow knitted-silk tie
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

desc:
Crafted in France from pure silk in a black shade, this Lanvin bow tie is assured and elegant. The subtle contrast of textures with the knitted front and woven back add the subtlest detail to evening outfits and demonstrate a command of black tie style.
  • Black layered knitted silk and plain-woven bow tie
  • Pre-tied style, adjustable neck strap
  • Hook and eye fastening
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Made in France

  • Navy silk tie
  • White polka-dot print
  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
  • Handmade in London, England

  • Dry clean
  • Made in Italy

desc:
Knitted ties are a classic addition to any wardrobe and this hand-finished version from Brioni will bring an air of finesse to any outfit.   • Dry clean

desc:

In the case of this self-tie Turnbull & Asser design, opt for a silk lapel with a slight sheen. A dress shirt, blazer and Cary Grant swagger will take you through the evening in impeccable style.

  • 100% silk
  • Dry clean
